Detailed Description

Structure for payload type.

Note
nPcmMode PCM Mode Setting.
0: No action(use previous PCM enable mode)
1: Auto mode(DSP will change to proper mode according to the voice codec attribute)
2: Narrow-band Mode
3: Wide-band Mode
